title: Bug 121682 - Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: Exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export the data from the table in the attached report, an exception is thrown at the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function.
EB: When exporting the data from the table, the data should be exported successfully without any exceptions.
SR:
Bug 121682 - Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Add a table with a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
3. Preview the report.
4. Attempt to export the data from the table.
